news.title: DM asks officials to remove obstacles for Patna metro project
news.para: In a meeting held with the officials of Delhi Metro Rail Project, the nodal agency of Patna metro project, and district officials, the DM reviewed the ongoing construction work of metro and obstacles faced in executing the project.

news.title: Ajmera Realty sales value up 19% in Q3 FY23
news.para: In 9M FY23, Ajmera Realty & Infra India has surpassed the total annual sales value of Rs 431 crore in FY22 by 1.6 times to Rs 694 crore.

news.title: Avadi corporation ignores NGT fiat to evict lake encroachers in Tamil Nadu
news.para: The civic body has 12 lakes within its jurisdiction. The National Green Tribunal (NGT) last year had directed state authorities to identify and remove all encroachments on lakes to avoid flooding.
